  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Results of recent studies on the importance of soft skills indicate that the single most important soft skill for a job candidate to possess is interpersonal skills, followed by the ability to negotiate and resolve conflict and written or verbal communication skills. In order to further increase our members&apos; employability, FUNDI has developed a soft skills role play training program which addresses the key challenges faced by our members when seeking work.</narrative>
